comments.content: RAS protein has three isoforms ( K,N and H RAS). the isoforms differ in ability of activating RAF protein, the isoform which is responsable the most of activating of Raf protein is Kras> also, HRAS has the ability of activating the RAF proteins but less efficiently than KRAS.
